cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on evaluating models of semantic similarity in Vietnamese. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural network models, which suggests it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves human judges rating degrees of similarity, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
